{"tid":248001,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"男人永遠都唔覺得自己有錯","createTime":"2017-05-18T08:29:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-18T11:05:01.000Z","uid":78960,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bef42bf6d33b26df82e75fb371b320102ad9b8c8","tid":248001,"uid":78960,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T08:29:16.000Z","msg":"講番背景 我同男朋友一齊六年<br />\n我地係long d<br />\n佢兩年前開始有第三者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到上年七月我忍唔住講分手<br />\n點知佢就好唔開心<br />\n又話要跳樓又話要死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我咪打比佢媽咪<br />\n好啦 到之後我想同番佢一齊 佢就唔肯<br />\n根本一直以黎都當我係雞<br />\n成日要我send淫相比你 又錄音淫叫比你聽<br />\n仲叫我求其搵多個人同你3p?<br />\n送野比你又嫌三嫌四<br />\n仲要當街打我？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係喇 你個第三者最好最了解你<br />\n咁你唔同佢一齊？仲講到冇咗佢都冇所謂咁<br />\n咪又係每次都番去搵佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實有冇諗過你出軌咁多次我仲肯同你一齊你應該珍惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連我啲朋友都唔想我同你一齊你冇諗過係你問題？<br />\n係你冇咗我唔得 冇咗我你又走去死<br />\n到你唔理個臭西 佢又話抑鬱又要死<br />\n你理得佢姐 咪由得佢死囉 佢抵死嫁<br />\n做得第三者就預咗嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我駡個臭西你仲要幫住佢？<br />\n你畢業之後番香港 你都係繼續同佢有聯絡嫁啦<br />\n你實心軟嫁喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解你可以搵個臭西我唔可以搵嗰個人？<br />\n根本就雙重標準<br />\n我真係好想公開個第三者啲資料 但係係咪要加密<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d03d52df9f1f9bab6dc70cd6d61d374b03894057","tid":248001,"uid":78960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T08:34:50.000Z","msg":"講到你要用錢貼我咁 個臭西何嘗又唔係貼緊你？<br />\n我駡走佢有咩問題<br />\n出軌出到好似你咁仲要上床又同居<br />\n你仲好意思駡我？"},{"pid":"d44d7ef2c5a20afdc327f68713a71c03761bd654","tid":248001,"uid":4531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T08:35:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fc4d6d31af98b3953716937c738ee35e077f5efa","tid":248001,"uid":15646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T08:37:41.000Z","msg":"爆料啦"},{"pid":"16f3fac95542d796234b50927789c470aa02a537","tid":248001,"uid":501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T08:44:01.000Z","msg":"痴線<br />\n自己出得軌就要自己承擔返個後果架啦<br />\n真係理得佢去死<br />\n咪由佢去死囉<br />\n仲要唔係第一次<br />\n<br />\n快手執野走人喇施主"},{"pid":"4bb9a11ded6c6aae3c7df978f62c2722daff53d1","tid":248001,"uid":67657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T08:45:48.000Z","msg":"想你公開個賤男資料多D"},{"pid":"6e2e1df31fa113b74623a45f3433bf5ba07e1e10","tid":248001,"uid":105693,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T08:46:12.000Z","msg":"咩事，連登依排多咁多聖人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你咁做已經寵壞佢啦，你話第三者話要死所以佢搵返人，咁佢話跳樓你又搵返佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講真，咁嘅男人你都肯要返，你咁冇自信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你覺得佢冇咗你要死，佢話唔定覺得你咁都信勁蠢<br />\n<br />\n仲話叫你send閃卡比佢睇，佢當你係咩。<br />\n<br />\n成件事根本冇考慮嘅餘地，認真諗下條友值唔值得你浪費青春。"},{"pid":"4acba559e9c1c3ee72f1d896b98fca000da7ee72","tid":248001,"uid":78960,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T08:48:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想你公開個賤男資料多D</blockquote><br />\n要爆啲咩😂 我都係想整死個臭西姐<br />\n唔想搞到男朋友 我驚我都會比人起埋😂"},{"pid":"58e989df41f4be7543f66a0da4b1d3badf00a0b0","tid":248001,"uid":78960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T09:05:43.000Z","msg":"之前成日話個臭西喺我丢低你嘅時候扶番你起身<br />\n人地想承虛而入炸！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講到佢真心為你咁 佢自己都同你講佢同你玩下嫁炸<br />\n佢比人趕出校係佢扺死<br />\n自己冇讀書都可以瀨落其他人到<br />\n你估佢真係因為你唔開心所以讀唔到？<br />\n你咁都信？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e306bc2f527825c0c284f93777ffe6a24639bdcf","tid":248001,"uid":54854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T09:09:30.000Z","msg":"你咁都肯同返佢一齊<br />\n某程度上你都係幫兇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54ffb40b7f4db58a4c02bca79caef8b7222e50f6","tid":248001,"uid":78960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T09:11:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你咁都肯同返佢一齊<br />\n某程度上你都係幫兇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我唔同佢一齊冇人要我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faddfe8f5a97a4f3617817b9e04f97915b4a6fd0","tid":248001,"uid":113828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T09:12:33.000Z","msg":"講真 有第三者已經可以同佢講永別"},{"pid":"aee98253eee0f38e2e85cc87cc07f251f98c9cb5","tid":248001,"uid":78960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T09:30:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n張相係個臭西ig<br />\n我都唔知我男朋友鍾意佢啲咩"},{"pid":"052a7b8f6ae6cbe85dee8de3dc4d388291dfaaba","tid":248001,"uid":14112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T09:32:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n張相係個臭西ig<br />\n我都唔知我男朋友鍾意佢啲咩</blockquote><br />\nPo埋名啦 佢不仁 你不義姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"084f24c26270acdc20435108985fd87c1ba1b85f","tid":248001,"uid":28624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T09:34:14.000Z","msg":"就眼睇似係男方既錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6b2d05d007bd834019ba500845d90b84e926b87","tid":248001,"uid":71712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T09:37:20.000Z","msg":"唔po埋自己我地點比較呀<br />\n條囡more"},{"pid":"c0a25ae6b06239b8dd380a33032e9d724bd01490","tid":248001,"uid":12994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T09:46:34.000Z","msg":"女人真係犯賤"},{"pid":"e37e0c3ecd749f6e49e8d81bf56038aa8a1bdbd6","tid":248001,"uid":78960,"like":0,"d